## NIBBLE-LEARN TOOLS PAGE OVERVIEW

### Page Layout

#### Top Navigation Bar
- **Logo**: Nibble-Learn logo (student version may have different color)
- **User Info**: Student name and avatar (top-right)
- **Room Indicator**: Shows which student room they're in
  - "Ms. Johnson's senior 5 math class"
  - Click to switch rooms (if in multiple)
- **Help Icon**: Question mark for student-friendly help

---

### Page Header

**Welcome Message**:
- **Text**: "Hi [Student Name]! 👋" or "Welcome to your learning tools!"
- **Typography**: 
  - Font Size: 1.5rem (24px)
  - Font Weight: Bold
  - Color: Purple or dark gray
  - Friendly, encouraging tone

**Current Room Display**:
- **Text**: "Ms. Johnson's Class" or current room name
- **Icon**: Classroom or people icon
- **Style**: Badge or pill
- **Color**: Light purple background

---

### Search Bar

**Layout**: Prominent, centered below header

**Search Input**:
- **Width**: 500-600px (desktop), full-width (mobile)
- **Height**: 52px
- **Placeholder**: "What do you want to learn today?" or "Search for a tool..."
- **Icon**: Magnifying glass (left side)
- **Border**: 2px solid light purple
- **Border Radius**: 26px (fully rounded pill shape)
- **Font Size**: 16px

**Search Features**:
- **Auto-suggest**: Shows matching tools as you type
- **Fuzzy Search**: Understands misspellings
- **Popular Tools**: Shows before typing starts
- **Categories**: Groups results by category

**Student-Friendly Language**:
- Instead of technical names, uses simple descriptions
- "Help me write an essay" → Essay Outliner
- "Study for my test" → Quiz Yourself, Study Partner

---

### Filter & Sort Section

**Filter Buttons** (Horizontal pills):
- **All Tools** (default, active)
- **My Favorites** (shows starred tools)
- **Recently Used** (last 5-10 tools)
- **Categories**: Dropdown or separate pills
  - Writing & Research
  - Reading & Learning
  - Math Help
  - Study Tools
  - Creative Tools

**Active Filter**:
- Purple background
- White text
- Slightly larger

**Inactive Filter**:
- Light gray background
- Dark gray text
- Hover: Light purple

---

### Tools Grid

**Layout**:
- **Desktop**: 3-4 columns
- **Tablet**: 2-3 columns
- **Mobile**: 1-2 columns
- **Gap**: 20px between cards

**Card Dimensions**:
- **Width**: Auto (fills column)
- **Height**: ~200-240px
- **Aspect Ratio**: Maintain consistent heights

