## TOOL CATEGORIES
Nibble-learn organizes 50+ tools into clear categories:

### 1. WRITING & RESEARCH (15-18 tools)
Focus: Help students with writing assignments and research projects

### 2. READING & LEARNING (8-10 tools)
Focus: Comprehension, vocabulary, and understanding texts

### 3. MATH HELP (6-8 tools)
Focus: Math problem-solving, step-by-step explanations

### 4. STUDY TOOLS (10-12 tools)
Focus: Test prep, flashcards, review materials

### 5. CREATIVE TOOLS (8-10 tools)
Focus: Stories, art, projects, presentations

### 6. AI LITERACY (4-6 tools)
Focus: Learning about AI, responsible use

