## COMMON TOOL INTERFACE DESIGN

Every student tool follows a consistent, student-friendly interface pattern:

### Tool Card (in grid view)

**Card Container**:
- **Size**: ~280-320px width, ~200-220px height
- **Background**: White
- **Border**: 1px solid light purple
- **Border Radius**: 16px (more rounded than teacher version)
- **Shadow**: Subtle, increases on hover
- **Padding**: 20px

**Card Content Structure**:

**Icon Area** (Top):
- **Icon**: Large, colorful icon (56-64px)
- **Background**: Gradient circle or none
- **Colors**: 
  - Writing tools: Blue gradient
  - Math tools: Green gradient
  - Study tools: Purple gradient
  - Creative tools: Pink/orange gradient
- **Position**: Top-left or centered

**Text Area** (Middle):
- **Tool Name**: 
  - Font: 1.125rem (18px)
  - Weight: Bold (700)
  - Color: Dark purple or black
  - Margin: 12px top
  
- **Description**:
  - Font: 0.875rem (14px)
  - Weight: Regular (400)
  - Color: Medium gray
  - Lines: 2-3 max
  - Student-friendly language (no jargon)

**Badge Area** (Top-right):
- **"New" Badge**: For recently added tools
  - Background: Green or purple
  - Text: "New"
  - Size: Small pill

**Action Area** (Bottom):
- **Try It Button** (appears on hover):
  - Text: "Try it" or "Open"
  - Style: Small purple button
  - Full width of card

**Hover State**:
- Lift: translateY(-4px)
- Shadow: Stronger shadow
- Border: Purple border
- Transition: 0.3s ease

---

### Individual Tool Page Layout

When student clicks on a tool, they see:

#### Page Structure: Side-by-Side Layout

**Layout**: Two-column design (60/40 split)

---

### LEFT PANEL: Input Section

**Width**: 40% of screen
**Background**: Light cream/beige or very light purple
**Padding**: 32px
**Sticky**: Stays in place while scrolling

**Panel Header**:
- **Tool Icon**: Large icon (48px)
- **Tool Name**: Bold, 1.5rem
- **Description**: 1-2 sentences explaining what the tool does
  - Student-friendly language
  - "This tool helps you..."

**Safety Reminder Banner** (if first time using):
- **Icon**: Shield or info icon
- **Text**: "Remember: Your teacher can see what you create!"
- **Background**: Light blue or yellow
- **Dismissible**: X button to close
- **Position**: Above form

**Input Form**:

Each input field follows this pattern:

**Field Label**:
- **Text**: Simple, clear question format
  - "What's your topic?" instead of "Topic"
  - "What grade are you in?" instead of "Grade Level"
- **Font**: 14px, Semibold (600)
- **Color**: Dark gray
- **Required Indicator**: Red asterisk if required

**Field Input**:
- **Type**: Text input, textarea, dropdown, or custom
- **Height**: 44-48px (text inputs)
- **Border**: 2px solid light gray
- **Border Radius**: 8px
- **Font Size**: 16px (prevents zoom on mobile)
- **Placeholder**: Helpful example text
  - "Example: The water cycle" instead of "Enter topic"

**Help Text** (below input):
- **Text**: Additional guidance in small gray text
- **Font**: 12px
- **Color**: Medium gray
- **Icon**: Info icon (optional)
- **Example**: "Tip: Be specific about what you want to learn!"

**Character Counter** (for textareas):
- **Display**: "0 / 500 characters"
- **Position**: Bottom-right of textarea
- **Color**: Gray (normal), Orange (near limit), Red (at limit)

**Generate Button**:
- **Text**: "Generate" or "Create" or "Get Help"
- **Style**: Large, purple button
- **Width**: Full width of form
- **Height**: 52px
- **Icon**: Sparkle or magic wand
- **Position**: Bottom of form
- **States**:
  - Default: Purple, enabled
  - Disabled: Gray (if form incomplete)
  - Loading: Purple with spinner, "Creating..."
  - Success: Brief green state

**Clear/Reset Button**:
- **Text**: "Start Over" or "Clear"
- **Style**: Text link or secondary button
- **Position**: Below generate button
- **Color**: Gray

---

### RIGHT PANEL: Output Section

**Width**: 60% of screen
**Background**: White
**Padding**: 32px
**Scrollable**: Yes

**Empty State** (before generation):
- **Icon**: Large tool icon or friendly illustration (120px)
- **Message**: "Your [output] will appear here!"
- **Emoji**: Friendly emoji (📝 ✨ 🎯)
- **Sub-message**: "Fill out the form on the left and click Generate"
- **Illustration**: Optional friendly character or scene
- **Color**: Light purple or blue

**Loading State**:
- **Spinner**: Large, animated spinner
- **Color**: Purple
- **Message**: "Creating your [output]..."
- **Sub-message**: "This usually takes 10-15 seconds"
- **Animation**: 
  - Pulsing dots or
  - Progress bar (if available) or
  - Fun animation (pencil writing, robot thinking)

**Output Display**:

**Output Header**:
- **Title**: "Your [Output Type]" or tool-specific title
- **Timestamp**: "Created 2 minutes ago" (small gray text)
