**Tool Card Design**:
- Large colorful icons (56-64px)
- Friendly, simple descriptions
- Student-appropriate language
- Category color-coding
- Hover effects (lift + shadow)

**Tool Interface (Standard)**:
- **Two-panel layout**: Form (40%) + Output (60%)
- **Student-friendly labels**: Questions instead of field names
- **Clear instructions**: "What's your topic?" vs "Topic"
- **Large buttons**: 48-52px height (touch-friendly)
- **Safety reminders**: Always visible
- **Help text**: Throughout interface

**Interactive Elements**:
- Chat interfaces for AI Tutor, Character Chat
