- Flashcard flippers with self-assessment
- Image generation with style selectors

### Safety & Monitoring:

✅ **Always-On Moderation**: PII detection, content filtering
✅ **Teacher Visibility**: All student work visible to teachers
✅ **Safety Reminders**: On every tool, persistent banners
✅ **Content Warnings**: Tool-specific (math errors, fact-checking, plagiarism)
✅ **Approval Workflows**: Flagged content reviewed before student sees
✅ **Redirect Screens**: For inappropriate requests

### Design Philosophy:

- **Student-Friendly**: Simple language, helpful examples, encouraging tone
- **Colorful & Engaging**: Gradients, illustrations, emojis
- **Safe by Design**: Multiple safety layers, teacher oversight
- **Educational**: Teaches responsible AI use while helping with schoolwork
- **Accessible**: Large text, simple navigation, high contrast
- **Monitored**: Teacher can view everything, real-time activity feed

This comprehensive system provides students with powerful AI learning tools while maintaining safety, educational value, and teacher control at all times.
